fao_sofi.source: FAO - State of Food Security and Nutrition Report

crime_index.note: Higher score = higher crime rate (lower safety)

pollution_index.note: Higher score = higher pollution (worse environmental quality)

airports.note: Total number of airports per country (infrastructure indicator)

unemployment.note: Unemployment rate as percentage of labor force (lower = better)
